response.original_title: Diona Doherty: Get Your Pink Back!
response.overview: Irish comedian Diona Doherty has lost her pink (we called it 'mojo' before the internet). She's pretty certain her kids are hiding it. Along with her abs. In her debut hour she is on a mission to get it back and prove that she can still have fun. As long as that fun ends by 9pm.
response.title: Diona Doherty: Get Your Pink Back!
